item.title: Queen - We Are The Champions - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song We Are The Champions by Queen from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: Adim7, Am, A♯, A♯m6, C, Cm, Csus4, Dm, D♯, D♯add9, Edim7, F, F7, Fm, F♯dim7, Gm7, Gsus4, G♯.

item.title: Audrey Hepburn - Moon River - Ukulele Cheats
